Use the standard library

This is how to solve of s:
   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this s's length times:
      Remember that c is item i in s
      When c is at least 97, then:
         When c is at most 122, then:
            Add result to diff of c and 32
         But, if not:
            Add result to c
         End when
      But, if not:
         When c is at least 65, then:
            When c is at most 90, then:
               Add result to sum of c and 32
            But, if not:
               Add result to c
            End when
         But, if not:
            Add result to c
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   When s's length is 4, then:
      Remember that reversed is []
      Remember that j is s's length
      Do this s's length times:
         Decrease j
         Add reversed to item j in result
      End do
      The answer is reversed
   End when

   The answer is result
